nodes.text: Star Wars Rebels Magazine 4 is the fourth issue of Star Wars Rebels Magazine. It was originally published by Egmont UK Ltd in the UK on April 22, 2015, and by Titan Magazines in the US on April 19, 2016. The UK version includes the comic story Kallus' Hunt by Martin Fisher and Bob Molesworth, while the US version includes the comic stories Eyes on the Prize and Sabotaged Supplies.
